    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208250/extras/d497b31387749095e515eade56ddca00.avif?t=1733869663\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208250/extras_big/d497b31387749095e515eade56ddca00.avif?t=1733869663 width=800 height=513 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Being a piece of bread, you naturally crave a stack of pancakes for breakfast. To start off your day and, more importantly, fill your stomach, you set off on a journey to get the best pancakes in town. However, you soon realize you have no clue where the bakery is. Thankfully, it seems like an intruder in your house may just know where you can find it...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208250/extras/e403a0b4e7bd6db28e1b0e03927c3627.poster.avif?t=1733869663\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208250/extras/e403a0b4e7bd6db28e1b0e03927c3627.webm?t=1733869663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208250/extras/e403a0b4e7bd6db28e1b0e03927c3627.mp4?t=1733869663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this casual platformer, you  explore environments ranging from your home to space. Though getting to your end goal doesn't seem   hard at first, you soon find that the path there is a tad convoluted, with enemy desserts jumping around at every turn, trying to stop you. Not to mention, your new friend seems to enjoy messing around with you a bit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208250/extras/6e45a7ec767560d00b47e1d8389152f1.poster.avif?t=1733869663\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208250/extras/6e45a7ec767560d00b47e1d8389152f1.webm?t=1733869663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208250/extras/6e45a7ec767560d00b47e1d8389152f1.mp4?t=1733869663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you're looking for a low-stress way to take a break, this may just be the game for you. :)</p>",
